      <p>An aggregated score, <italic>R</italic>
<sub><italic>ij</italic></sub>, is calculated using the weighted Stouffer’s method:<disp-formula id="Equ3"><label>3</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M11">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
